attr.title: Candy Girl official video New Edition 1983
Murphstar Live from Breakfast of Champions 2012
attr.description: "Wow!Another AMAZING Breakfast of Champions:Sunny Skies, a Funktion One sound system, street closure and thousands of revelers rocking in the first day of the year.Thanks again to the Space Cowboys for starting 2012 off right and for having me play.It is always the best party of the year.The 11:00 am set outside inspired a little jazzy swing and electro house with equal parts diva vocals and dirty baselines and a few classics thrown in for good measure. Hope you all enjoy it." - Murph
